  (NULL, 'The practice is always right here, always now, always available.', 167, 123, '2025-11-18T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Counting breaths is training wheels for presence. Eventually, you won''t need them.', 156, 112, '2025-12-13T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Nature, sun, rain, quiet walks, the sound of birds. We need these. We are these.', 189, 145, '2025-11-17T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'The world will always offer distraction. You must choose presence.', 198, 156, '2025-12-14T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'If you don''t schedule stillness, chaos schedules itself.', 178, 134, '2025-12-11T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'The body meditates. The mind just needs to stop interfering.', 167, 123, '2025-12-13T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'In the practice, there is no competition. Only compassion.', 145, 98, '2025-11-07T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Each sit is complete in itself. There is no accumulation.', 134, 89, '2025-12-05T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'What changes in meditation is not the world but how you hold it.', 189, 145, '2025-11-07T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Real transformation is invisible. It happens in the quiet moments.', 178, 134, '2025-12-20T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'The stillness beneath thought is always present. Always accessible.', 167, 123, '2025-11-27T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Close your eyes to see what truly matters.', 156, 112, '2025-10-16T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'The first step is sitting down. Everything else follows.', 189, 145, '2025-10-18T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'In silence, the heart speaks.', 198, 156, '2025-10-13T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'The only way out is in. Meditation shows the door.', 234, 167, '2025-12-27T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'When the doing stops, being begins.', 178, 134, '2025-12-06T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Consciousness doesn''t need improvement. Just recognition.', 167, 123, '2025-11-30T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Expectation is the thief of presence.', 189, 145, '2025-10-28T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Trust the process even when you can''t see the path.', 145, 98, '2025-10-16T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'The mountain doesn''t strain to be still. Neither should you.', 178, 134, '2026-01-01T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Gently. That''s the only instruction you need.', 156, 112, '2025-10-18T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Sit as if you have nowhere else to be. Because you don''t.', 198, 156, '2025-12-30T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'The less you grasp, the more you receive.', 167, 123, '2025-12-12T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'What you feed grows. Feed your attention to presence.', 189, 145, '2025-11-17T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Between stimulus and response, there is a pause. Make it yours.', 234, 167, '2025-12-21T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'You are already whole. This practice is remembering, not becoming.', 178, 134, '2025-12-28T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'In the beginner''s mind, there are many possibilities. In the expert''s, few.', 198, 156, '2025-10-19T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Labels limit. Awareness liberates.', 145, 98, '2025-11-17T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Let thinking happen without becoming the thinker.', 167, 123, '2025-10-23T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Meditation is the daily practice of coming home to yourself.', 189, 145, '2025-12-01T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'The joy of sitting in silence is its own reward.', 156, 112, '2025-12-09T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Each time you choose stillness, you strengthen the muscle of attention.', 178, 134, '2025-12-08T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'There are no experts in presence. Only practitioners.', 167, 123, '2025-12-08T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'The inner world is vast. Explore it.', 145, 98, '2025-12-25T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'What resists in meditation is what needs the most attention.', 189, 145, '2026-01-04T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Be as gentle with your wandering mind as you would with a child learning to walk.', 234, 167, '2025-12-13T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Nothing to achieve. Nowhere to arrive. Nothing to become.', 178, 134, '2025-12-14T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Healing happens in the space between effort and surrender.', 198, 156, '2025-11-01T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'The quiet is not empty. It is full of answers.', 167, 123, '2026-01-02T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Show up. Sit down. Let go. Repeat.', 156, 112, '2025-11-04T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'The path and the destination are the same thing: presence.', 189, 145, '2025-10-14T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Sit like the mountain. Breathe like the ocean. Observe like the sky.', 234, 167, '2025-10-14T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Awareness is the ground. Everything else is weather.', 178, 134, '2025-12-02T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'This moment is the only meditation there is.', 198, 156, '2025-11-26T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'The practice is not about perfection. It''s about showing up anyway.', 167, 123, '2025-12-12T11:02:02.579Z'),
