  (NULL, 'The heart opens when the mind softens.', 178, 134, '2025-11-28T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Awareness is the simplest thing. That''s what makes it so hard.', 167, 123, '2025-12-24T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Silence teaches what words cannot convey.', 156, 112, '2025-10-14T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Behind every thought is the thinker. Behind the thinker is awareness.', 189, 145, '2025-11-04T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'What seems like nothing happening is everything shifting.', 198, 156, '2025-12-24T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Quieting the mind is not the goal. Observing the mind is.', 178, 134, '2026-01-05T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'In the practice, you find what you didn''t know you were looking for.', 167, 123, '2025-10-13T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Every breath is an invitation to begin again.', 234, 167, '2025-10-16T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'The greatest journey is the one that leads back to yourself.', 189, 145, '2025-10-10T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'In stillness, you discover you were never lost.', 178, 134, '2025-11-06T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'This breath. Right now. That''s the only practice there is.', 198, 156, '2025-11-19T11:02:02.579Z'),
  (NULL, 'Come home to the breath. Come home to yourself.', 167, 123, '2025-11-16T11:02:02.579Z'),
